===Noun===
'''steel''' {{uncountable}}

# A [[metal]] [[alloy]] of mostly [[iron]] plus [[carbon]], harder than pure iron but [[malleable]] when hot.
# A tool used to [[sharpen]] or [[hone]] [[knives]].
# A [[sword]]. 

